title: Tomáš Huber
text: Tomáš Huber (born 29 August 1985) is a <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech</a> professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28football%29">defender</a>, who currently plays for <a href="FK%20DAC%201904%20Dunajsk%C3%A1%20Streda">FK DAC 1904 Dunajská Streda</a>.
